        <Parent_String>Amphibia (class) [300249665], Vertebrata (subphylum) [300265720], Chordata (phylum) [300266513], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order of amphibians characterized by larvae lacking true teeth and external gills, adults being tailless and having elongated hind limbs modified for jumping, and a single frontoparietal and no lacrimal bone in skull. Dates from the Middle Jurassic to present, including two extinct and 28 or more extant families with over 5,400 living species.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Orde van amfibieën die wordt gekenmerkt door larven zonder echte tanden en uitwendige kieuwen, volwassen dieren zonder staart en met lange achterpoten, speciaal aangepast voor het springen, en een schedel met één frontopariëtaal deel en geen traanbeen. Leefde reeds in de vroege Jura en omvat twee uitgestorven en 28 of meer nog levende families met circa 5400 soorten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>屬兩棲動物，其特徵為幼體無真齒，亦無外鰓；成體無尾，後肢修長以利跳躍，具單一額頂骨，頭骨中無淚骨。無尾目源自侏儸紀中期，其中兩科已絕跡，現存的科則有二十八種以上，含超過五千四百種物種。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Orden de anfibios caracterizado por larvas que carecen de dientes verdaderos y branquias externas, los adultos no tienen cola y tienen extremidades posteriores alargadas modificadas para saltar, y un solo hueso frontoparietal y sin hueso lagrimal en el cráneo. Fechas desde el Jurásico Medio hasta el presente, incluidas dos familias extintas y 28 o más existentes con más de 5.400 especies vivas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000320/GRI-FloCo</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109721/GRI, FloCo terminology (2019-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tecuanimeh tlen nemihpan atl axquipiyah inintlancoch huan iyacatzol ica iixpa, tlen motlahtlantoqueh axquipiya inincuitlapil, quipiyah ininicxi huan ininmahmah huehhuehueyac tlen ica huitonih, zan ce omitl tlen pan itzontecon, huan axquipiya omitl ipan iixtiyol yon icuaomiyo. Ipan cahuitl jurasico media huan azta naman ome tlamantli quechpechimeh poliuhtoc huan 28 tlamantli tlen itztoqueh ica quence 5400 tlamantli nemih.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
